    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a pretty strong take. When you talk about this \"destabilization,\" do you see this as a threat to the actual mechanics of democracy, like voting and law, or is it more about the \"otherness\" you mentioned—like these groups being unable or unwilling to integrate into the existing system?",
