      "content": "The initial wave of demographic change will primarily translate to a political upheaval, with minority groups primarily seeking representation and policy influence to address their perceived grievances. I fear a loss of authority for the existing power structure, as newly empowered constituencies push towards a more permissive, identity-based politics. The stability of voting systems, institutions, and laws will be less threatened by demographic shifts than the ideological underpinnings of the culture they inhabit – white America's tradition of dominance.",
